<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="467" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1436,1617,1750]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1653,1678]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was originally described as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName box="[1008,1184,1653,1678]" class="Reptilia" family="Gekkonidae" genus="Afroedura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="transvaalica">
<emphasis box="[1008,1184,1653,1678]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="467">A. transvaalica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but was elevated to specific status without comment by Branch (
<number box="[697,757,1690,1714]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" value="1998.0">1998</number>
), although 
<bibRefCitation author="Kluge" box="[898,1055,1689,1714]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" refString="Kluge, A. G. (2001) Gekkotan lizard taxonomy. Hamadryad, 26, 1 - 209." type="journal article" year="2001">
Kluge (
<number box="[989,1047,1690,1714]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" value="2001.0">2001</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
continued to recognize it as a subspecies.
</paragraph>
